			Peace to all, I’m Julia and I do want to share something to my fellow readers. When I was still a 7th grader, I experienced a hearing difficulty. When I reached high school I was already using a hearing aid. But I’m not totally deaf; it’s just that I only hear a minimal amount of sound from my surrounding. When I started working after the graduation in college, I find it hard to travel to and from the office where I worked. That is why I decided to learn how to drive and finally obtained a driver’s license even if I have a difficulty in hearing.
<br />;<br />;Only last January of 2010, I managed to have a car loan from one of the <a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL2xpc3Rvbm5ldC5jb20v" target="_blank">;dealership</a>;  that I found online. Well I visited their office first, talked to their sales manager who was very friendly and very accommodating upon seeing that I was wearing a hearing aid. But she asks me first if I have a driver’s license, when I showed hear my license we then continue our discussion with regard to my plan to avail with their car financing program.
<br />;<br />;They offered me a <a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL2xpc3Rvbm5ldC5jb20vaW5kZXgucGhwP3BfaWQ9Mw__" target="_blank">;2008 Suzuki XL7</a>; . Even though it’s a used car, it’s still astonishing and beautiful. They told me that I can take their car loan program. Just with $3000 down payment, I can have the Suzuki and payable within 72-months. When my loan was approved days after, I immediately went to the <a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL2xpc3Rvbm5ldC5jb20vaW5kZXgucGhwP3BfaWQ9MQ__" target="_blank">;dealership’s</a>;  office and drove home with my car. Oh by the way, I put a Domestic-scale induction loop in my car to help me in my driving so that I can hear other car’s sirens or even to that of a police officer.
<br />;<br />;It’s hard at first in my part when driving because I can’t hear things around me clearly. Also it’s a little bit dangerous but as time goes by I can now drive as much as a normal driver can.
